{
  "description": "worker_roles.default × Pattern C (ephemeral or gitignored_repo_root sub-mode). Worker_dir = `<workers_dir>/<task_id>/` (ephemeral) or `<existing_repo_root>/` (gitignored sub-mode). No base_clone; the sub-mode-specific worker_dir is captured at dispatch time via --worker-dir. additionalDirectories adds the knowledge/raw carve-out at {claude_org_path}/knowledge/raw (per §5.1). Pins per docs/contracts/role-pattern-sandbox-contract.md §4.3.",
  "inputs": {
